A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending the Lopez family; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, the Lopez family's unwavering resilience in the face of adversity demonstrates
3 their outstanding strength and determination to fight for what is right; and
4 WHEREAS, despite being denied a second medical opinion, being criminally charged, and
5 losing custody of their children due to false accusations, the Lopez family remained united
6 in the pursuit of justice; and
7 WHEREAS, through tireless advocation, they not only fought for the return of their own
8 children but also worked to change the legal system, ensuring that other families would not
9 have to endure the same hardship; and
10 WHEREAS, through the family's perseverance and determination, all charges on them were
11 dismissed, leaving a legacy that serves as an example of hope and optimism for families in
12 similar situations; and
