13 WHEREAS, Kelly Lopez's testimony was instrumental in advocating for the implementation
14 of Georgia Senate Bill 259, that provides updated procedures for when a family is suspected
15 of abuse or neglect; and
16 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the contributions of this family be
17 appropriately honored.
18 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
19 recognize and commend the Lopez family for their tireless advocation on behalf of families
20 in the State of Georgia.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
22 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Lopez Family.
